title: Didn't get level 39 and level 40 rewards
body: Hey, its been a while since I reached level 39 and 40 and while I have gotten notifications for the rewards they are not in my loot tab.

replies.body: No worries, I gotchu fam. I was able to line up the times of your levelups and capsules to see what happened, and you should now see those capsules in your loot ^_^
